    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in solid, good condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a great luster, though upon close inspection, you will notice some minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scratch near the driver-side door handle. Inside, the interior is very clean and free of odors, with only light wear visible on the driver\u2019s seat bolster and floor mats. Mechanically, the car is sound, performs reliably, and comes with a consistent service history, offering a great balance of value and longevity for the next owner.",
