    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty! It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014it's always been garaged, there isn't a single scratch on it, and the interior still smells brand new! It drives like an absolute dream and has been treated with so much love. I'm sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to be obsessed with it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
